Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:36.70,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said, if you ain't lendin' me money,\Nthen no date today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:40.62,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'd be okay\Nif you finally put out instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.08,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for the love hotel, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.46,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be punched!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:52.67,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.93,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.39,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.81,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yer broke and ya ain't puttin' out!\NGet lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.98,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.65,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Octopus! Squid! Tuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:11.98,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totes funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:16.55,BD Center Right,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(603.333333,261.666667)}EPISODE 1\NTHAT'S HOW LOVE STARTS, YA KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.48,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seafood names aren't insults.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:19.11,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, comfort me!\NHe was my first boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.53,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to not go for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.95,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was so good about him, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.91,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like Ken Takakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.96,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, there you go.\N- You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:32.79,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing wrong with that!\NI like masculine guys like Ken Takakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.38,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I am an awkward fellow, after all."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.26,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dudes like that are extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.22,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.47,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will I not be able to meet\Nanother Mr. Ken in my lifetime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.10,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, someone comfort me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.65,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:56.78,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn it!\N- You missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.53,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I did miss.\N- Don't look over here. Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.95,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- We have this, too.\N- Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.95,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put a magnet inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.62,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This'll hurt, won't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.00,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you reading there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.67,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.80,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,BIRTH OF THE AEROSPACE SELF-DEFENSE FORCE\NGUARDING OUTER SPACE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.64,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.02,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do only scum live in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.06,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.90,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I relieve all this stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.40,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Momo Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.74,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.36,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:45.41,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.24,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many times you gonna say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:52.00,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like Miss Ayase talking to me?\NThat's gotta be the only reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.04,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you got the wrong idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.55,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I wanna get\Nchummy with you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.59,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.55,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:04.93,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The President has already gone to Mars!\NWhat is the entirety of Project Pegasus!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:05.89,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.93,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fan of the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:11.14,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't believe in UFOs or aliens\Nor stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.60,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about a UFO, but a UAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:17.65,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,PO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:16.15,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unidentified Aerial Phenomena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.65,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're being a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:23.03,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The U.S. military has officially acknowledged\Nthe existence of UAPs and reformed the Space Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.57,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japan has also newly created\Nan Aerospace Defense Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.49,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Any way you look at it,\Nthey're getting ready for Space Wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.83,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:30.66,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.58,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait! This has the newest image\Nof Nessie, too. Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.59,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It also talks about Lieutenant Colonel\NJim Channon and Skinwalker Ranch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.46,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:45.09,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got dumped\Nso I don't want any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.47,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How you push stuff at me is so typical\Nof otaku and really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.52,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have no friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.14,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me like you know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.66,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.92,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,YOUR TRUE POWERS AND POTENTIAL\NHAVE YET TO AWAKEN...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.84,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.68,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.52,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I do believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.52,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, there's no such thing as ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.77,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I matched the conversation topic to yours,\Nbut you outright deny that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.61,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mock the occult!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:50.53,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know,\Nmy grandma is a spirit medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.24,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:55.00,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever seen exorcism?\NIt's really wicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.17,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The possessed person goes into convulsions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.29,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can go into convulsions from illness, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.09,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not proof that ghosts are out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:06.51,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then have you ever had\Nan alien let you ride a UFO!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.22,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your logic is jumping too far!\NAre you an idiot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.68,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.23,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She gave up on Ken Takakura\Nand went after an otaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.40,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look. It's like she doesn't care\Nwhat other people would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.02,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't say I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.03,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's have a contest, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:28.49,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there really are ghosts,\Nyou'll be serving me as a gofer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.82,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you UFOs, I mean, UAPs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:36.00,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're able to see one, M-Miss Ayase,\Nyou'll be my gofer instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.83,BD DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,NAGI GENERAL HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.38,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,OCCULT-KUN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.71,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?\NIt's way too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.22,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is a UFO hotspot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.34,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nagi Hospital there is called\Nthe sanctuary for UFOs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.64,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you call for a UFO on the roof,\Nyou will experience Abduction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.73,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's Abduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.56,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's when an alien kidnaps you\Nand experiments with your body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.78,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on! Have you been\Nexperimented on before!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.65,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is a chance that I have!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.32,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:12.99,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Many people who experience Abduction\Nhave their memories erased.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.62,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you. You've never seen\Na UFO before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.37,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you know about regressive hypnosis?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.08,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.21,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not an issue\Nof whether or not you've seen one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:24.08,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The point is whether or not\Nthere's proper proof that it exists!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.34,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.71,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.18,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.23,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,KEEP OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.23,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the spiritual hotspot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.15,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll go and prove it right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.78,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that there are no such things as ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.49,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you aren't freaking out, are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:55.83,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, that spot is famous on the 'net\Nfor something definitely being there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:14.59,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too shy, shy boy, in this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.85,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say speaking loudly\Nis the most dangerous thing to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.72,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too shy, shy boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.68,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the 'net.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.43,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been mentioning the 'net a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.40,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So have you seen a ghost, Miss Ayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.11,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.98,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.69,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How dare you talk so authoritatively earlier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.90,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.78,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take back that attitude\Nyou've been giving me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:37.20,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's absurd that you've never\Nseen a ghost but believe in them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.29,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.66,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you my grandma's a spirit medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:46.13,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love my grandma a lot\Nsince I don't have parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.38,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.42,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting all meek and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:57.64,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get a load of this.\NMy family is seriously weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.06,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I always had to perform\Na good luck ritual before stepping outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.64,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was always forced to do it\Nthe entire way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:09.44,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course,\NI was the laughingstock of all the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.86,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do it, Grandma got pissed.\NIt was the pits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:16.32,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the toughest part of it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:20.45,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was when the boy I liked\Nmade fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.79,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really hated my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:27.67,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Because of that weird ritual,\Nthe boy I like hates me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.00,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I said something horrible\Nlike that to Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:37.55,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I didn't talk to Grandma until recently,\Nand I stopped doing the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:43.27,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I get pissed when someone else\Nmakes fun of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.85,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.11,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hate the fact that\Nthe boy I liked didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:56.03,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hated the fact that the boy I liked\Nmade fun of my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:02.99,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, I loved both Grandma and her job\Nas a spirit medium, because it felt special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:08.67,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How she decided to take me in,\Nand lovingly raised me all by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.13,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith in my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.59,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:18.43,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, why do you believe in aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.97,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That really doesn't matter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.81,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?\NYou don't have any reasons?
