Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:37.94,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I can't bring myself\Nto speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:42.07,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way. Why is my heart racing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.15,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This can't be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.16,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was just surprised because he happened\Nto recite one of Ken Takakura's lines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.91,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to calm down for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.66,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:58.00,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrible at remembering names.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.96,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.42,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ken Takakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.55,0:22:10.05,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,DAN
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:10.30,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,DAN DA
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.97,BD Top DX,On-screen Text,0000,0000,0000,,DAN DA DAN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:44.19,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aliens really did exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.73,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts exist, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.19,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The existence of aliens and ghosts\Nbeing proven means that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.65,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there's a possibility of supernatural\Nphenomena, UMA,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:52.62,BD DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and all other things that were said to be absurd\Ncan be proven as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:52.62,BD Top DX,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine, I get it! Ready.
